title: Cathe Friedrich - Lean Legs & Abs DVD-R NTSC [ISO]
description:
This lower body toning and shaping workout uses both innovative and traditional exercises to shape the thigh muscles. Although all parts of the thigh muscles are used in Lean Legs & Abs, most of the emphasis is placed on the quadriceps and outer thigh muscles to provide the perfect complement to our Great Glutes workout. The sequence in Lean Legs & Abs is designed to keep your heart rate up while incinerating your thighs and revealing your inner six pack. The segment breakdown is as follows: Warm Up; Compound Legs; Chair/Firewalkers; Core; Stretch; and Bonus Barre. Do all of the segments for the most comprehensive results.

Main Workout:

Warm Up - 6:10
Workout - 36.44
Stretch - 5:39

Premixes:

61:11 Lean Legs and Abs + Bonus Barre: (Warm Up, Compound Legs, Chair/Firewalkers, Bonus Barre, Core, Stretch)

55:00 Lean Legs and Abs + Bonus Barre (No Core): (Warm Up, Compound Legs, Chair/Firewalkers, Bonus Barre, Stretch)

50:00 Lean Legs and Abs + Bonus Barre (No Chair/Firewalkers): (Warm Up, Compound Legs, Bonus Barre, Core, Stretch)

37:23 Timesaver #1 (No Chair/Firewalkers): Warm Up, Compound Legs, Core, Stretch)

38:24 Timesaver #2 (No Core): Warm Up, Compound Legs, Chair/Firewalker,Stretch)

35:40 Timesaver #3 (Chair/Firewalkers & Barre): Warm Up, Chair/Firewalkers, Barre, Stretch)

Done as ISO as there are premixes on this DVD.

Equipment Needed: Hand Weights, Resistance Loop
